  "texts": [
    "It is said that the Monitor Hypothesis predicts faster outcomes for adults compared to children.",
    "The goal of the Monitor Hypothesis is to explain how the acquired system is influenced by the learned system.",
    "When second language learners monitor their speech, they apply their understanding of the learned grammar to edit, plan, and initiate their communication.",
    "This action can only occur when speakers have sufficient time to consider the form and structure of their sentences.",
    "The amount of monitoring occurs on a continuum."
  ],
